<section class="reviews mod book-content">
    <header>
        <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr" 
            data-isverify="False"
            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/1002931/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            胡适文集（7卷）的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 6 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6131557">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6131557/" class="title-link">该怎样追寻胡适</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6131557"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/36771726/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36771726-14.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36771726/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">唐山</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-06-23"
      class="main-meta">2013-06-23 18:56:35</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6131557_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  胡适的文集，这些年来颇出版了一些，花城出版社的这个版本不求全，但最有影响的文章基本在内，易得、易看，对非专业研究者，是不错的读品。  在中国现代史上，胡适与鲁迅堪称双峰并峙，那时的中国有太多需求，革命也许是必然选择，在今天，我们不应站在和平的背景下指责革命，...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">10有用 / 2没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            花城出版社2013版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6131557_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6131557_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2034665">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2034665/" class="title-link">历史是现代科学的方法论</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2034665"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/tomyen/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2477682-14.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tomyen/" class="author">
